flowchart TD
  Starting ~~~ Unpausing
  Stopping ~~~ Paused
  Stopped ~~~ Deleting

  Starting -->|booted| Running
  Running -->|pause or auto-pause| Paused
  Paused -->|resume| Unpausing
  Unpausing -->|restored| Running
  Running -->|stop requested| Stopping
  Stopping -->|complete| Stopped
  Stopped -->|start| Starting
  Running -->|delete requested| Deleting
  Paused -->|delete requested| Deleting
  Stopped -->|delete requested| Deleting
  Deleting -->|cleanup complete| Deleted
